<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="howl-vi">howl <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /haʊl/    美 /haʊl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(狗、狼等) 嚎叫；嚎哭；怒号：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One theory is that wolves howl to bond better together.
一种理论认为狼嚎是为了更好地团结协作。</p><footer>2011 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>howled in</strong> pain as I dropped the hammer onto my foot.
锤子砸在了我脚上，我疼得大叫。</p><footer> 外研⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The wind howled through the trees.
风在林间怒号。</p></div></div>